original_title: EXCRETION: The Shocking True Story of the Football Moms
overview: The climb of 90s punk band The Football Moms to the top is an epic tale of abuse, betrayal, and extremely unhygienic music. Will singer Cozy Deathbed survive chronic wet brain to emerge a winner? Or will he and his band of misfits fulfill every rock band cliche'? This movie tells all--and more.
title: EXCRETION: The Shocking True Story of the Football Moms
